description:
乾坤大挪移可以在运行时动态添加属性。请实现 `__getattr__`：

```python
class MingCultist:
    def __init__(self, name):
        self.name = name
        self._skills = {}

    def __getattr__(self, attr):
        if attr in self._skills:
            return self._skills[attr]
        return f'{attr}未学会'

    def learn(self, skill_name, skill_desc):
        self._skills[skill_name] = skill_desc
```

创建 MingCultist('张无忌')，learn('乾坤大挪移', '运行时改变一切')，然后输出 zwj.乾坤大挪移。

输出：`运行时改变一切`

